{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-recipe-post-js","path":"/白斩鸡/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"一本食谱"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"50ca3efb-f59a-5018-96f7-a5075ac68827","excerpt":"食材 2 人份 做鸡肉的材料 材料 量 备注 三黄鸡 1000g  姜 4 ～ 6 片  葱 2 根 可不放 八角 2 个 可不放 料酒 适量  做蘸料的材料 材料 量 备注 姜末 少量  蒜末 少量  香菜碎 适量  蒸鱼豉油 适量  步骤 准备…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/1d0fd/image.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.12658227848101%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"白斩鸡\"\n        title=\"白斩鸡\"\n        src=\"/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/828fb/image.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/ff44c/image.jpg 158w,\n/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/a6688/image.jpg 315w,\n/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/828fb/image.jpg 630w,\n/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/0ede0/image.jpg 945w,\n/a-cookbook/static/d6e646c65e3186bc123db643664a2f64/1d0fd/image.jpg 974w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>食材</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2 人份</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5>做鸡肉的材料</h5>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">材料</th>\n<th align=\"left\">量</th>\n<th align=\"left\">备注</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">三黄鸡</td>\n<td align=\"left\">1000g</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">姜</td>\n<td align=\"left\">4 ～ 6 片</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">葱</td>\n<td align=\"left\">2 根</td>\n<td align=\"left\">可不放</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">八角</td>\n<td align=\"left\">2 个</td>\n<td align=\"left\">可不放</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">料酒</td>\n<td align=\"left\">适量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h5>做蘸料的材料</h5>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">材料</th>\n<th align=\"left\">量</th>\n<th align=\"left\">备注</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">姜末</td>\n<td align=\"left\">少量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">蒜末</td>\n<td align=\"left\">少量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">香菜碎</td>\n<td align=\"left\">适量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">蒸鱼豉油</td>\n<td align=\"left\">适量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>步骤</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>准备 2 大锅纯净水（水量要能完全盖过鸡），没有大锅就把鸡一分为二</li>\n<li>一个锅中加姜、八角、葱，煮沸放料酒</li>\n<li>水开后，拎起鸡，放入锅中烫一下就提起，重复 3 次</li>\n<li>把鸡整个放入锅中，开盖煮 1 分钟，捞出放入另一口锅冷水浸泡后捞出</li>\n<li>再次放入锅中开盖煮 4 分钟</li>\n<li>盖上锅盖煮 1 分钟后关火，根据鸡的大小焖 40—50 分钟</li>\n<li>捞出冷却（如果要脆皮的口感，捞出后浸泡在冰水中 10 分钟）</li>\n<li>需要皮色金黄的话，抹上香油</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>备注</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>煮鸡的汤可以用来煮面、馄饨，做汤底</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"白斩鸡","date":"July 12, 2022","description":"肉质很嫩","contributors":["Markmum"],"tags":["中餐","鸡肉"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/五分钟面包/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"五分钟面包"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/无糖无油紫薯软欧包/无糖无油紫薯软欧包/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"无糖无油紫薯软欧包"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"50ca3efb-f59a-5018-96f7-a5075ac68827","previousPostId":"9ca0e3e7-da6f-5361-95bd-b5dae3677a25","nextPostId":"87978d73-0c03-502b-9dd0-12c607dad48e"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2297725318","2841359383"]}